OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Facross the region tonight with plenty
OL,7,Fof clear spells, especially across
OL,8,Fcentral and eastern parts. Potential
OL,9,Ffor some sea fog in northern Cornwall
OL,10,Fand Devon. Temperatures will fall
OL,11,Funder the clear spells to give a
OL,12,Fpatchy rural frost.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FAfter a chilly start, it will
OL,15,Fbe another warm day with light winds.
OL,16,FMore cloud is expected than on
OL,17,FSaturday, but there will still be
OL,18,Fplenty of bright spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
