OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FStaying largely dry at the start of
OL,7,Fnext week with light winds and some
OL,8,Fwarm sunshine. Chilly nights. A
OL,9,Fcooling easterly breeze developing by
OL,10,FWednesday, and perhaps isolated
OL,11,Fshowers later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
